				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Ok, here's a question nobody ever seems to ask....
<br />

<br />

<br />
So SCM saves you 2.5%, 7.5%, and 15%  On whatever is your main specialization (200).  What about the abilities that are not your main?  I.E. the other specializations that remained 50 like Abjuration, Alteration, Divination etc.
<br />

<br />
I don't know if I have ever seen hard numbers on what your mana savings are with specialization level 50 by themselves.  I have heard around 2% or something, but I don't know for sure.<br />_________________<br /><Center><b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=36994" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sage Eandori Raintree</a></b>
